name: Untitled Memory #0003
description:
Untitled Memory #0003 by Jett Roxx | 2021 | Photomanipulated GAN Painting

In a methodology calling into the collective subconscious, Jett Roxx's 'Untitled Memories' revisits the mundane, now tangled into one another, setting new forms of familiarity yet far-off obscurities. Set in saturated tones, AI-generated figures formed from collective imagery set from user-sent pictures now present themselves new. What follows are pseudo memories that question us about their existence. Did these memories hold a name in the past? Are the users only letting go now due to the effects of time and eventual degradation? Nonetheless, as specimens now with new user names, they are captured again.
